Solution?  Fentanyl analogues.  Synthesis is not too tricky, precursors =
are obtainable to the determined.  3-Methyl Fentanyl is a opoid similar =
to Heroin only about 300 times more potent placing its activity in the =
20 microgram range, one kilo, well distributed, is enough to intoxicate =
50 million people!  Its so active it could be placed on blotter paper.  =
The cops could never stop the tide of 3 independant chemists each =
channeling thousands of grams of fentanyl all over the country.  The end =
would be a matter of time.

atek3



